#: ../../source/fundamentals/circular-dependency.rst:120
msgid ""
"The module reference has a ``get()`` method which allows retrieving a "
"provider available in the current module. Additionally, you can switch to"
" a non-strict mode, which enables you to pick any existing provider among"
